cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB. 

This paper is about generating natural language descriptions from a structured knowledge base, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and databases (cs.DB) as it deals with generating descriptions from structured data.
